{"tid":1000974,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我係咪好絕情","createTime":"2019-01-29T21:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T09:06:36.000Z","uid":218954,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"edb0a5f09155b50bb68491c7f4d5c52b24350d05","tid":1000974,"uid":218954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T21:32:44.000Z","msg":"今晚失眠，諗起分手無耐嘅ex<br />\n而我竟然一啲都記唔起同佢嘅感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如諗起同佢一年前去旅行<br />\n我所有細節都記得，但個畫面就係無咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗起同佢同居咗4年嘅屋企<br />\n記得晒喺嗰度生活嘅點滴，但就係唔記得佢個人<br />\n<br />\n散咗只係幾個月，我連佢個樣都開始唔太記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但明明一齊嘅5年入面，我係好愛好愛佢，諗住同佢一世㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然行到最後幾個月都猶豫痛苦咗好耐，但個心決定分手嗰刻，當下就放低晒一切，對佢嘅愛同恨都瞬間消失晒<br />\n<br />\n再諗諗下，我對每個ex都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當下好投入，但過咗去就唔好話留戀，直頭去到失憶嘅地步<br />\n<br />\n最後其實好對唔住個ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢仲好痛苦但我已經忘記咗佢嚕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115265adcd7416db1a67d07c1b2a4cadc0fd9f01","tid":1000974,"uid":159532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T21:38:14.000Z","msg":"都好既，起碼唔會留戀過去。"},{"pid":"c437b0e2adc933046b779422e918f3d8ab923c89","tid":1000974,"uid":17179,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T22:36:14.000Z","msg":"原來感情真係可以話無就無"},{"pid":"ba6ce67fdc42feb63903736459ffd8b1d4175849","tid":1000974,"uid":210758,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T23:06:22.000Z","msg":"反正都返唔到轉頭，諗嚟有冇用？"},{"pid":"4c48bd164025d52cbdd501d6c0e85f94dd2c35b4","tid":1000974,"uid":218954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba6ce67fdc42feb63903736459ffd8b1d4175849","tid":1000974,"uid":210758,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T23:06:22.000Z","msg":"反正都返唔到轉頭，諗嚟有冇用？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T23:22:00.000Z","msg":"諗返都開心嘅<br />\n不過就係為發生過嘅事開心<br />\n而唔係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fccc3169bd3ed8511cdff353e4f967fe686354bd","tid":1000974,"uid":38662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T07:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db096641001b89b9a73d1654f8feb5b5b3327beb","tid":1000974,"uid":14374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:58:44.000Z","msg":"咁你拍拖真係唔怕失戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e912ca5f37712b27182142692f41ee7bb089b9","tid":1000974,"uid":68363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T09:06:36.000Z","msg":"一個對左你咁耐既人都可以冇咩印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}